OL,3,CInspectors will visit Iran's nuclear
OL,4,Csites, UN says, despite mixed messaging
OL,6,FInspectors will visit Iran's nuclear
OL,7,Fenrichment sites, the United Nations
OL,8,Fnuclear agency has said.
OL,10,FThe ability for the UN to assess the
OL,11,Fsites is a key part of the interim
OL,12,Fdeal between the US and Iran in
OL,13,Freaching an end to the war.
OL,15,FThe comment by International Atomic
OL,16,FEnergy Agency (IAEA) head Rafael
OL,17,FMariano Grossi was the firmest yet
OL,18,Ffrom the agency, which is important in
OL,19,Fdetermining the status of Iran's
OL,20,Fnuclear stockpile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
