OL,3,CInspectors will visit Iran's nuclear
OL,4,Csites, UN says, despite mixed messaging
OL,6,FThe statement from the UN comes as the
OL,7,FUS and Iran have made contradictory
OL,8,Fremarks about whether the enrichment
OL,9,Fsites would be inspected.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FUS Vice President JD Vance said on
OL,17,FMonday that Tehran had agreed to admit
OL,18,Fnuclear monitors into the country
OL,19,Ffollowing talks in Switzerland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
