PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782290901
OL,3,CInspectors will visit Iran's nuclear
OL,4,Csites, UN says, despite mixed messaging
OL,6,FSince Israel launched a 12-day war on
OL,7,FIran in 2025, the IAEA has been
OL,8,Fblocked by Tehran from visiting
OL,9,Fenrichment sites where the Islamic
OL,10,FRepublic is believed to store enough
OL,11,Fhighly enriched uranium to potentially
OL,12,Fbuild as many as 10 nuclear weapons.
OL,14,FIran has long maintained that its
OL,15,Fprogramme is peaceful and is attended
OL,16,Ffor nuclear energy, even though it is
OL,17,Fthe only country in the world to have
OL,18,Furanium enriched up to 60% purity
OL,19,Fwithout a weapons programme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
